reviewText: Informative, disturbing facts about abortion industry and the growth in the Pro Life movement among the younger generation.

The movie shows how abortion harms, not helps, women, and what has been done to stop it. The important thing they forgot to mention, is the high rate of suicides following abortion. Seven times the number of women who take the lives of their babies, as those who give birth to them, commit suicide. Abortion is not good for women. See the movie and learn why.
